The '''United Council of Bith Musicians''' was a splinter group of [[Bith/Legends|Bith]] [[Musician/Legends|musicians]]. They came under the influence of the [[Alien/Legends|alien]]-rights [[Diversity Alliance]] and pledged their support by playing songs that exposed the goals and ideals of the Alliance as well as [[Anti-Humanism|anti-Human]] propaganda while touring alien [[Planet/Legends|worlds]].

While [[Nolaa Tarkona]] was displeased at having the service of musicians instead of more [[Soldier/Legends|soldiers]], her Adjunctant Advisor [[Hovrak]] suggested to her that they could be used to help incite anti-human riots or coups against Human or pro-Human authorities.

